 --------------------------------------------------------------\n\n \n\nDea
 r Motivational Monday Community\, 🎉\n\n \n\nThe time has come! The neve
 r-ending learning journey begins and what better way to start the week tha
 n with motivating and newly learned material that you can share with other
 s. 🤩\n\n \n\nAs promised\, we will present a learning unit on the topic
  of New Work Style every Monday.\n\n \n\nWe want to learn together with yo
 u\, as we incorporate highly relevant topics and updates. To make it a Win
 -Win situation we will practice the Fridays for Future Work Sessions with 
 you\, or in other words\, give you a sneak peek\, so you already know what
  to expect from the participants. 😉\n\n \n\nWe're looking forward to a 
 great learning experience with you and we'll see you on \n\nMotivational M
 onday\n\n \n\nYour GUIDEs\n\nCarsten & Guenter\n\n\n\n\n__________________
